data.description: Fantastic find in Dallastown School District! Loads of features. Beautiful kitchen which includes a dining area overlooking the backyard. Kitchen features granite counters, large island and pantry. Gas fire place in nice size living room. Office and formal dining room on main floor. 4 beds/3.5 baths. Primary bathroom includes walk-in closet, double vanity sink, soaking tub and tile shower. Finished lower level boasts family room, wet bar and theater room; perfect for entertaining. Rear deck and great size yard. 2 car garage. Gas heat/ central air. Great location. A joy to own!
